      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">BOTANIC GARDENS SYDNEY ¶ N.S.W ¶ . ¶ Letterhead printed around the British crown. ¶ Botanic Gardens ¶ Sydney, 10th March, 1885 ¶ Baron F. Von Mueller...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">85.03.10a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John McLachlan</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Richardia stellaris</seg> (MEL 2268397), accompanied by an unsigned draft in M's handwriting of a letter to Joseph Hooker; see M to J. Hooker, 11 March 1885 (in this edition as 85-03-11a).</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">BOTANIC GARDENS SYDNEY</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.S.W</seg>
               <seg>.</seg>
               <seg>
                  <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">Letterhead printed around the British crown.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Sydney, 10th March, 1885</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron F. Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On receipt of your letter<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> yesterday morning I placed it in Mr Betche's hands, who immediately went to Mossman's Bay,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Sydney Harbour.</p>
               </note> where he found flowering specimens of the new rubiaceous plant, which I send you by today's mail. This plant grows on the top of a flat sandstone hill near to Mossman's Bay, remote from all houses and gardens. The top of the hill is mostly bare rock, with the exception of a thin layer of humus formed of decayed mosses in the shallow cavities of the flat rocks. A dense green turf covers this layer, and the plants found in it are principally <name key="Cynodon">Cynodon</name>, <name key="Killingia">Killingia</name>, and the specimen now forwarded to you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I regret we have not any fruiting specimens of <name key="Haloragis%20salsoloides">Haloragis salsoloides</name>; nor has Mr Betche ever yet found a living plant of this species.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr Moore returns via Melbourne, and he is expected to arrive there sometime during this week.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Charles Moore was returning to Sydney from a period of leave in Europe.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I am, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John McLachlan</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Clerk</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Cynodon">Cynodon</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Haloragis%20salsoloides">Haloragis salsoloides</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Killingia">Killingia</name>
            </p>
         </div>
